reporter-output.line: Test Initiated
Launch chrome browser
Open trivago.de page
EnterHotelnameOrDestination field is detected and destination name 'Hamburg' is entered
FromCalenderMonth element is detected and date is selected
ToCalenderMonth element is detected and date is selected
SearchButton element is detected and clicked. This will wait to fetch the hotel list
List of hotels searched in the city on Homepage of trivago.de is displayed
Unser niedrigster Preis element is detected and clicked
Option from Angebote is selected and the selected hotel detail is opened in a new tab
Post this step, the security blocks further execution via automated scripts
